body_html:
I got tensorflow on 25 Jan. On that date, the mnist_deep.py program specified shape=[None] for the y_ parameter. Clearly something changed that was not obvious to someone innocently reading the documentation online.

It would be very helpful if the new online documentation for Iris examples had clear date/version information on the python code they refer to in case someone changes the underlying code again.
